import React from 'react'
import Icon3 from '../../images/image7.svg'
import Icon8 from '../../images/image8.svg'
import Icon9 from '../../images/image9.svg'
import InstagramEmbed from 'react-instagram-embed'
import {
  ServicesContainer,
  ServicesH1,
  ServicesWrapper,
  ServicesCard,
  ServicesIcon,
  ServicesH2,
  ServicesP,
} from './ServicesElements'

const Services = () => {
  return (
    <ServicesContainer id="services">
      <ServicesH1>Some of my latest Youtube videos</ServicesH1>
      <ServicesWrapper>
        <ServicesCard>
          <iframe
            width="450"
            height="315"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TJXxhTgKrso"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
          ></iframe>
        </ServicesCard>
        <ServicesCard>
          <iframe
            width="450"
            height="315"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qVA4frN2X_0"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
          ></iframe>
        </ServicesCard>
        <ServicesCard>
          <InstagramEmbed
            url="https://www.instagram.com/p/CJgFZINhYwp/"
            maxWidth={320}
            hideCaption={false}
            containerTagName="div"
            protocol=""
            injectScript
            onLoading={() => {}}
            onSuccess={() => {}}
            onAfterRender={() => {}}
            onFailure={() => {}}
          />
        </ServicesCard>
      </ServicesWrapper>
    </ServicesContainer>
  )
}

export default Services
